      "content": "everything i’ve been doing feels so pointless. we’re fighting a tide that’s just too big. no matter how many protests we hold or how many people we reach, the system just absorbs it all and keeps going. i feel like i’m just wasting my life for a cause that’s already dead. i don't see the point in even trying anymore.",
