      "content": "a \"spark\" sounds nice but it's just a metaphor. in reality, people just move on from a protest or a speech in a week. if you want to actually shake the foundation, you need something that creates an unavoidable crisis. something that forces the world to look at the rot. i just don't see any way for an individual to have that kind of leverage anymore. everything feels so heavy and stagnant.",
